Package net.tfobz.vocabletrainer.gui.panels

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    VocableTrainerBarPanel
    VocableTrainerBarPanel is a GUI component that represents the menu bar in the Vocable Trainer application.
    VocableTrainerCreditsPanel
    VocableTrainerCreditsPanel is a GUI panel that displays the credits for the Vocable Trainer application.
    VocableTrainerHomePanel
    The VocableTrainerHomePanel class represents the home screen panel of the Vocable Trainer application.
    VocableTrainerInfoPanel
    VocableTrainerInfoPanel is a GUI panel that displays and manages vocabulary sets within the Vocable Trainer application.
    VocableTrainerMenuPanel
    The VocableTrainerMenuPanel class represents the main menu panel within the Vocable Trainer application.
    VocableTrainerNewPanel
    VocableTrainerNewPanel is a GUI panel that allows users to create new vocabulary sets, import/export sets, rename or delete existing sets, and add new vocabulary cards.
    VocableTrainerPanel
    Represents the main panel of the Vocable Trainer application.
    VocableTrainerRunPanel
    VocableTrainerRunPanel is responsible for managing the vocabulary training session.
    VocableTrainerSettingsPanel
    VocableTrainerSettingsPanel is a GUI panel that allows users to configure settings for the Vocable Trainer application.
    VocableTrainerStartPanel
    The VocableTrainerStartPanel class represents the starting panel of the Vocable Trainer application.
